text: Ðis syndon þa landgemaore to wasinga tune.
Ærest on duhan lea of duhan lea on readan wylle.
Of readdan wille to lydgeardes broge.
Of lidgeardes beorge to tatmonnes apoldre.
Of tatmonnes apoldre to deneburge hleawe.
Of deneburge hleawe to stan beorge.
Of þam hlæwe to here grafe of here grafe to twam beorgum.
Of twam beorgum to hremnes dune.
Of heremnes dune to bidan holte.
Of bidan holte þæt to wigan campe.
Of wigan campe to bennan beorge.
Of þam beorge to blæccan pole.
Of þam pole to þære apuldre þonne to dunan heafde.
Ðis synt þa den þe þærto gebyrigeaþ.
Wynburgespær & þreo crochyrsta & horsham & yffeles leah & hæslwic & gatawic & ridan fald & scacalwic & hundsæding fald.
